Class AttributeConstraintsTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.jelly.TagSupport
      • org.kohsuke.stapler.jelly.AttributeConstraintsTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.commons.jelly.Tag

    public class AttributeConstraintsTag
extends org.apache.commons.jelly.TagSupport
    DTD-like expression that specifies the constraints on attribute appearances.

    This tag should be placed right inside <st:documentation> to describe attributes of a tag.

    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi
